short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Automatically logs into Google when clicking a GCP URL from external apps.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This Chrome extension automatically logs you into a pre-configured Google account when you click on a GCP Console URL from Slack or other external applications.
